text: Lukyanovsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Utyagulovsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 50 as of 2010. There is 1 street.Карта Зианчуринского района Башкортостана == Geography == It is located 89 km from Isyangulovo, 24 km from Utyagulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Lukyanovsky
